trans-unit.source: The type of element on the stack.
trans-unit.target: 堆疊上的項目型別。

trans-unit.source: Represents an immutable stack.
trans-unit.target: 表示不可變的堆疊。

trans-unit.source: **NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
trans-unit.target: **NuGet 套件**：<see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">關於固定集合及其安裝方法</see>)

trans-unit.source: This type is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 此型別具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Removes all objects from the immutable stack.
trans-unit.target: 從不可變的堆疊移除所有的物件。

trans-unit.source: An empty immutable stack.
trans-unit.target: 空的不可變堆疊。

trans-unit.source: Gets an empty immutable stack.
trans-unit.target: 取得空的不可變堆疊。

trans-unit.source: An empty immutable stack.
trans-unit.target: 空的不可變堆疊。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the immutable stack.
trans-unit.target: 傳回可逐一查看不可變堆疊的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator that can be used to iterate through the stack.
trans-unit.target: 可用來逐一查看堆疊的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether this instance of the immutable stack is empty.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，這個值表示此不可變堆疊的執行個體是否為空的。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if this instance is empty; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果這個執行個體是空的，則為 <see langword="true" />；否則即為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the object at the top of the stack without removing it.
trans-unit.target: 傳回堆疊頂端的物件而不需移除它。

trans-unit.source: The object at the top of the stack.
trans-unit.target: 堆疊頂端的物件。

trans-unit.source: Removes the element at the top of the immutable stack and returns the stack after the removal.
trans-unit.target: 移除不可變堆疊頂端的項目，並在移除之後，傳回堆疊。

trans-unit.source: A stack; never <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 堆疊；永遠不會 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The value to remove from the stack.
trans-unit.target: 要從堆疊移除的值。

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified element from the immutable stack and returns the stack after the removal.
trans-unit.target: 從不可變的堆疊中移除指定的項目，並在移除之後，傳回堆疊。

trans-unit.source: A stack; never <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 堆疊；永遠不會 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The object to push onto the stack.
trans-unit.target: 要推送至堆疊的物件。

trans-unit.source: Inserts an object at the top of the immutable stack and returns the new stack.
trans-unit.target: 在不可變堆疊頂端插入物件，並傳回新的堆疊。

trans-unit.source: The new stack.
trans-unit.target: 新的堆疊。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 可用來逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員是明確介面成員實作，

trans-unit.source: It can be used only when the <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableStack%601> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> interface.
trans-unit.target: 只有在 <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableStack%601> 執行個體轉換成 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> 介面時，才能使用這個成員。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 物件，可用於逐一查看集合。
